{"tid":1759512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸借錢黨出沒小心","createTime":"2019-11-27T16:41:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T17:29:12.000Z","uid":326483,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1841c5a7fc70d58211856df9fe1eebf36176fb0d","tid":1759512,"uid":326483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:41:19.000Z","msg":"前幾日夜晚落街食飯就有個大陸人問我借錢，開頭佢無直接開口借錢，見我識少少普通話就同我傾計同埋關心我之後先開始發動攻勢，會主動握你手又用各種話術想我借錢比佢，我自己又傻傻地信左佢。我知呢排兩地關係好敏感，我開頭都唔想借，但我果日自己落單，衰自己心太軟又唔識拒絕人，佢講野實在太勁，希望大家唔好落井下石，我當比錢交學費，只希望各位自己小心！<br />\n<br />\n佢有留低微信同電話比我<br />\n微信：chenghuaqiang88<br />\n電話：5763 9362（已經打唔通）<br />\n<br />\n如果遇到記住影佢相聯絡埋我，希望可以捉到佢！"},{"pid":"816e96fad7fdcc162b72c70043b3d0fab4e2530b","tid":1759512,"uid":326483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:47:07.000Z","msg":"Sorry電話number打錯 係5763 9326"},{"pid":"057410b3c75a69dc567e90dd6c6b0d5294e899db","tid":1759512,"uid":25557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:47:14.000Z","msg":"明知呃錢心咩軟，冇L用"},{"pid":"c8b21503720f53a119811ad631bbcf0779240b42","tid":1759512,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連登仔唔會有同情心同理心，所以借錢黨唔會搵到佢哋笨。"},{"pid":"7320cb2b7e38e4eed5359c41df2a61975b8efc4e","tid":1759512,"uid":326483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"057410b3c75a69dc567e90dd6c6b0d5294e899db","tid":1759512,"uid":25557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:47:14.000Z","msg":"明知呃錢心咩軟，冇L用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:49:21.000Z","msg":"我都知我無L用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都唔知自己點解會肯借比佢"},{"pid":"82f15a6d83ca129595c405d21d199328dda79657","tid":1759512,"uid":2950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:50:22.000Z","msg":"出沒咗幾年喇屌"},{"pid":"628d1bb3d1e1247352569637b98655682c1f4825","tid":1759512,"uid":93717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor